            "body": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/25185 addresses this by not transferring the win-local options to a normal window if the float window has `style=minimal`. ~~Should we go further and skip that behavior for all floatwins, not only `style=minimal`.~~\n\nDecision from chat: only skip for style=minimal, since this is a special case and want to keep it limited rather than applying even more broadly.",
